{"tid":122762,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[求救] 養狗新手 狗狗嘔左三日 點算好😫","createTime":"2017-02-16T10:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T12:20:18.000Z","uid":6886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fac853093b4c3cf39e59c7e5eac42dce54482dac","tid":122762,"uid":6886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T10:01:19.000Z","msg":"我隻狗三日前開始嘔。<br />\n每次食完飯之後，隔一陣就會嘔返哂啲糧出嚟。<br />\n我觀察左一兩次，<br />\n見佢嘔出黎啲野除左一pat啡色(似係糧既色)之外，<br />\n仲有啲一粒粒好似冇咬過既糧。<br />\n我以為佢係食得太快，消化得唔好，<br />\n所以就一餐分開兩次餵。<br />\n但情況都好似冇乜好轉到。<br />\n<br />\n我今日再睇佢啲嘔吐物，<br />\n見到有一堆毛巾既線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該係個死女包咬爛自己條毛巾，<br />\n又鐘意乜都食哂落肚，<br />\n就食鬼哂毛巾甩出嚟既線。<br />\n而家佢訓左喺我隔離，<br />\n聽到佢個肚有啲googoo聲(好似係人肚餓打鼓嗰種聲)。<br />\n我上網睇post，啲人話餓佢一日，<br />\n等佢嘔清哂就得。<br />\n但我第一次養狗，真係唔識處理呢啲情況。<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲都曾經有類似既情況？<br />\n可唔可以請教下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁既情況算唔算嚴重？<br />\n係咪應該要帶佢去睇獸醫？"},{"pid":"48436e18c3105aa131de39670eb4edd086b25d93","tid":122762,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T10:23:48.000Z","msg":"如果佢真係食咗條毛巾<br />\n就要開刀<br />\n你帶佢睇下醫生先啦"},{"pid":"7d97518da2715b2ab7a996d05caa94a2c1286343","tid":122762,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T10:30:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果佢真係食咗條毛巾<br />\n就要開刀<br />\n你帶佢睇下醫生先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗多數都食咗（部分）條毛巾<br />\n如果係，樓主得一個選擇，睇獸醫吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而做手術你預有心理準備一定貴<br />\n<br />\n利申：ex女朋友隻聖班納成條食咗條毛巾，做手術開刀使費連住宿用咗兩萬機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80bdf8b87dec7ff086ef908930d66fdce1835685","tid":122762,"uid":6886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T10:41:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果佢真係食咗條毛巾<br />\n就要開刀<br />\n你帶佢睇下醫生先啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我諗多數都食咗（部分）條毛巾<br />\n如果係，樓主得一個選擇，睇獸醫吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而做手術你預有心理準備一定貴<br />\n<br />\n利申：ex女朋友隻聖班納成條食咗條毛巾，做手術開刀使費連住宿用咗兩萬機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢又冇食哂成條毛巾既...<br />\n係咬爛左條毛巾，<br />\n側邊甩線嗰啲位佢咬出嚟吞落肚...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下面附上圖...有啲核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/16/184048_dafd04885b0b1dee79c40960eadf43cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F16%2F184048_dafd04885b0b1dee79c40960eadf43cb.jpg&h=58cf6027&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/16/184054_6ec1daf355b852ee1a0ca149cecf363d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F16%2F184054_6ec1daf355b852ee1a0ca149cecf363d.jpg&h=786fdc73&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04d7c332bb7dcdb9283214fe878e2b679ccc364e","tid":122762,"uid":7952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T10:43:29.000Z","msg":"睇獸醫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb9ba39d39aa862a0a8bc09a0dbe0df2954d3fcc","tid":122762,"uid":6886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"頭先佢再嘔多次既時候，嘔左啲淺啡色有小小啫哩狀既水，裡面仲有啲佢自己既毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"787f872dc7eabe992d157753e1f38524c35a8ddf","tid":122762,"uid":32370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T10:47:20.000Z","msg":"狗間唔中嘔好正常，不過你尼個情況係食親野都嘔，可能係塞住個胃。唔洗諗，睇獸醫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c1bc3ac79f5e4c525980a43037500677521d71","tid":122762,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T10:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭先佢再嘔多次既時候，嘔左啲淺啡色有小小啫哩狀既水，裡面仲有啲佢自己既毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇睇醫生睇下咩事 買定領養"},{"pid":"da75b923a3abcf7ae0a3362642a1b3a7d2ec90d2","tid":122762,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T10:53:31.000Z","msg":"睇獸醫啦，仲問"},{"pid":"42b6e0d335744c8120da664b8134211736492ba5","tid":122762,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:04:13.000Z","msg":"咩狗，幾歲？<br />\n餵左幾多糧？"},{"pid":"d8883008c48f291932b7e0f89fdae48bb2b09c4b","tid":122762,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:28:24.000Z","msg":"如果係幾個月果啲bb 狗，用暖水浸淋左啲糧先俾佢<br />\n<br />\n毛巾唔好吞太多都ok嘅，太多真係要開刀攞返出嚟"},{"pid":"31d3f454261b3d0a2fcbcb5e11810a8a96c0de01","tid":122762,"uid":6886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:50:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩狗，幾歲？<br />\n餵左幾多糧？</blockquote><br />\n拉布拉多 一歲 <br />\n一餐大概大半杯至一杯"},{"pid":"cc68fd02a29b69847aafd6dc15512ca263578bbe","tid":122762,"uid":6886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:51:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果係幾個月果啲bb 狗，用暖水浸淋左啲糧先俾佢<br />\n<br />\n毛巾唔好吞太多都ok嘅，太多真係要開刀攞返出嚟</blockquote><br />\n好的，唔該哂🙏🏼"},{"pid":"d864196c423f9ba30318ed07ba4c80510fa67d72","tid":122762,"uid":6886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:52:55.000Z","msg":"如果真係要睇獸醫，大家有冇邊間推薦？<br />\n利申 我只係一個學生 budget有限😭"},{"pid":"51fc1cc6933477201529db3ad45354a0ae6af75f","tid":122762,"uid":46228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:55:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果真係要睇獸醫，大家有冇邊間推薦？<br />\n利申 我只係一個學生 budget有限😭</blockquote><br />\n去NPV啦<br />\n生命嚟，你問人借就要帶佢睇架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbca358f750861dce49b3139e23a3ad8814bf29a","tid":122762,"uid":6886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:03:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果真係要睇獸醫，大家有冇邊間推薦？<br />\n利申 我只係一個學生 budget有限😭</blockquote><br />\n去NPV啦<br />\n生命嚟，你問人借就要帶佢睇架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n就算我問財務公司借，我都一定會死啲錢醫佢。我係怕有啲係咪都作你一筆既獸醫診所，最後錢又比佢呃哂，狗又醫唔好姐。<br />\nBtw thanks for the advice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a12887f8a1381c8e72144708573ce2f2f260dd4e","tid":122762,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:14:12.000Z","msg":"佢以前係咪食開呢隻糧？<br />\n<br />\n如果仲有胃口，行得玩得又唔洗太擔心<br />\n試吓減量再浸左佢食睇吓得唔得<br />\n<br />\n當然擔心都俾獸醫睇睇啦，反正你一年都要打一次針"},{"pid":"5796ce5ec49f09438246a6133d7cf5c140acecb8","tid":122762,"uid":44897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T12:20:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩狗，幾歲？<br />\n餵左幾多糧？</blockquote><br />\n拉布拉多 一歲 <br />\n一餐大概大半杯至一杯</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n就到就試吓分三餐<br />\n計返重量睇吓每日餵幾多糧"}]}